


```bash
conda create -c conda-forge -p /mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc
_simu/geant4 geant4
```


先在大盘给g4创个环境，-p后指定物理路径，不能再用名字激活，只能用路径激活


```bash
$ conda activate /mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc
_simu/geant4
$ conda deactivate
$ conda config --set env_prompt '({name}) ' # 环境只显示名字不显示老长一串的路径
```
cmake安装
```bash
conda install -c conda-forge -p /mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4 cmake
```

进入项目后
```bash
cd /mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4/share/Geant4/examples/basic
git clone git@github.com:S200331082/scatterCorrection.git
cd scatterCorrection
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DZLIB_INCLUDE_DIR=/mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4/include -DZLIB_LIBRARY_RELEASE=/mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4/lib/libz.so -DFREETYPE_INCLUDE_DIR_freetype2=/mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4/include -DFREETYPE_LIBRARY_RELEASE=/mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4/lib/libfreetype.so -DEXPAT_INCLUDE_DIR=/mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4/include -DEXPAT_LIBRARY_RELEASE=/mnt/data03/users/fanghaodu/envs/mc_simu/geant4/lib/libexpat.so
# 长是长了点，但没有警告
make -j4
source ../run.sh

# cmake时不用管install路径，make install是make之后复制文件用的，对于手编的geant4才会有geant4-install这个文件夹
```

